text: Tavrovskoye rural settlement is a municipality in the Belgorod district of the Belgorod region of Russia. The administrative center is the village of Tavrovo. == History == Tavrovskoye rural settlement was formed on December 20, 2004 in accordance with the Law of the Belgorod Region No. 159. == Notes == == Other websites == * Official website of the administration * Rural settlement on the site of the Belgorod region Category:Settlements in Russia
